creator: KWS SAAT SE &Co.KGaA
descriptionHtml:
Start with an overview of your fields

Monitor the vitality of your plants

Optimise your silage corn harvest with satellite analysis*

Mark locations with important information

Mark your fields with just a few clicks

Use our weather forecast for farming

Check current market data for your business

Get seasonal tips and recommendations



Use our free tools and services to optimise your cultivation and make even better use of the genetic potential of the varieties. Get helpful data and recommendations for relevant decisions - from sowing to harvest for sugarbeet, maize, cereals, oilseed rape and other crops.

IT'S THAT SIMPLE:
- Mark your fields
- Define crop type and variety
- Immediately receive vitality data
- Discover more tools and services

PARTICULARLY USEFUL IN THE FIELD
Did you discover damage on your field? Is this the spot to take a soil sample soon? Are there any other specialties to keep in mind. With the new Field Scout, you can mark locations with pinpoint accuracy and add notes for later on.

KEY FEATURES
- Field management with satellite-based analysis
- Determination of vitality (NDVI) and dry matter (maize)*
- Location-related notes incl. appendix and reminder function
- Weather service adapted to agriculture needs
- Seasonal information and recommendations from our experts
- Direct contact to your regional consultants


*depending on regional availability
